column2: "Place the steaks on the grill and cook until golden brown and slightly charred
column3: 4 to 5 minutes. Turn the steaks over and continue to grill 3 to 5 minutes for medium-rare (an internal temperature of 135 degrees F)
column4: 5 to 7 minutes for medium (140 degrees F) or 8 to 10 minutes for medium-well (150 degrees F)."
